  <!-- FAQ -->
  <div style="margin-bottom:28px;">
    <div class="ab-lbl">Frequently asked questions</div>
    <div class="ab-faqs">
      <div class="ab-fq">
        <button class="ab-fqbtn" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">Is this site free to use?<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg></button>
        <div class="ab-fqbody">Yes &mdash; all calculators, charts, and guides are completely free with no registration required. The site is supported by non-intrusive advertising. We do not sell user data or require any personal information.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="ab-fq">
        <button class="ab-fqbtn" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">Do you collect my health data?<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg></button>
        <div class="ab-fqbody">No. All calculations run entirely in your browser. Nothing you enter is sent to our servers, stored, or shared. See our <a href="privacy.html" style="color:var(--accent);">Privacy Policy</a> for full details.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="ab-fq">
        <button class="ab-fqbtn" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">How accurate are the calculators?<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg></button>
        <div class="ab-fqbody">We use validated peer-reviewed formulas standard in clinical settings. Results are population-level estimates &mdash; individual variation of &plusmn;10&ndash;15% is normal. Use results as a starting point and adjust based on real-world feedback over 2&ndash;3 weeks.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="ab-fq">
        <button class="ab-fqbtn" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">Can I use this for medical decisions?<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg></button>
        <div class="ab-fqbody">No &mdash; content on this site is for informational and educational purposes only. It is not a substitute for professional medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment. Always consult a qualified healthcare provider before making health decisions.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="ab-fq">
        <button class="ab-fqbtn" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">What is the Asian BMI standard?<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg></button>
        <div class="ab-fqbody">The standard WHO BMI thresholds were derived from European population data. Adults of Asian descent develop metabolic health risks at lower BMI values. The WHO recommends a lower overweight threshold of BMI &ge;23 for Asian adults. Our <a href="asian-bmi-calculator.html" style="color:var(--accent);">Asian BMI Calculator</a> applies these thresholds.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="ab-fq">
        <button class="ab-fqbtn" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">Can I suggest a new calculator?<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg></button>
        <div class="ab-fqbody">Absolutely. <a href="contact.html" style="color:var(--accent);">Send us a message</a> with your suggestion &mdash; we review all feedback and have added features based on reader requests. We aim to respond within 48 hours.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
